

# 🌾 AgriConnect

[![Build Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/build-passing-brightgreen)](https://github.com/yourusername/agriconnect/actions)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue)](LICENSE)
[![Java](https://img.shields.io/badge/java-11%2B-blue)](https://openjdk.org/)
[![Selenium](https://img.shields.io/badge/selenium-4.x-brightgreen)](https://www.selenium.dev/)

**AgriConnect** is a digital platform connecting farmers, suppliers, and consumers via a secure, user-friendly agricultural marketplace. It supports product listings, communication, and efficient trade for a modern farming community.

---

## 📌 Navigation

- `Home`  
- `About`  
- `Marketplace`  
- `Contact`  
- `Login` / `Signup`  
- `Get Started`  
- `Browse Marketplace`  
- `Terms` / `Privacy`

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

### 🌐 Web Platform
- **Frontend:** HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (React or Vue optional)
- **Backend:** Java Spring Boot, REST APIs
- **Database:** MySQL / PostgreSQL
- **Authentication:** JWT / OAuth2

### 🧪 Test Automation Stack
| Tool             | Purpose                          |
|------------------|----------------------------------|
| Java             | Test scripting language          |
| Selenium WebDriver | UI browser automation           |
| TestNG           | Test framework                   |
| ExtentReports    | HTML test reporting              |
| WebDriverManager | Driver management (optional)     |

---

## 🧪 Test Project Structure

### ✅ Test Coverage Includes:
- Navigation flows (Home → About → Marketplace → Contact)
- User Login & Signup
- Browse & filter marketplace products
- Form submission (Contact)
- Legal page access (Terms & Privacy)

